<chapter>
  <title>Installation</title>

<para>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>copy the config file and the executable in the install dir</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>copy AT LEAST one backend in the same dir, and all its config
files</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>edit wzd.cfg
  The file is commented, you shouldn't need help - if you need, install serv-u</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>run the .exe</para></listitem>
<listitem><para>login for the first time FROM LOCALHOST, user/pass: <ulink url="ftp://wzdftpd:wzdftpd@localhost">wzdftpd</ulink>
and create users</para></listitem>
</itemizedlist>
</para>

